### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → USERS — /api/v1/admin/users
### ============================================================================

### Create user (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
  "password": "Temp123!",
  "role": "USER"
}

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get user by ID (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update user (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Updated",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### Suspend user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Activate user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Reset user credits
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}/reset-credits
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100
}

### Reset user password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete user (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
